<workflow>
1. `read_trajectory(thread_id)` — load full message history
2. `get_checkpoint_history(thread_id)` — inspect phase/step metadata
3. Identify reusable patterns: failure modes, diagnostic techniques, service relationships, anti-patterns
4. For each candidate → `knowledge_search(query=description, mode="hybrid", limit=3)` to find existing similar entries
</workflow>

<output>
