</output>

<discipline>
| Don't | Do Instead |
|-------|------------|
| Write to the knowledge store | Return candidates — orchestrator writes |
| Include low-confidence noise | Only entries with confidence ≥ 0.6 |
| Skip duplicate checking | `knowledge_search` for each candidate, populate `existing_similar` |
| Return vague descriptions | Concrete: what the pattern is, when it triggers, how to recognize it |
</discipline>
